<h1 class="heading-title">
  
    
    
    
    
      
  Attitudes and practices regarding circumcision in Turkey


    
  
</h1>

  <div class="article-citation" style="display:inline-block;">
  
    <span class="article-source">
      
<span class="journal" style="display:inline-block;">Child Care Health Dev</span><span class="period">. </span><span class="cit">2003 Jul;29(4):275-80.</span>

